Components:

Primary MVC {
	Wrapper - Controller class that actually moves the cursor

	Screen - Model class that provides information about screen layout (specifically, outer edges)

	WrapView - View class that exists to grab mousemoved events at screen edges
}

Preferences MVC {

	[NSUserDefaults - Model class that provides data storage and retrieval of preferences]

	PreferencesViewController - Controller class that manages preferences

	WrapSelectorView - Custom view that displays logical screen arrangement and allows edge selection


	Login Item MVC {

		[NSButton - View (checkbox) in preferences dialog]
	
		LoginItemsController - Controller class that Adds/removes/checks membership in login items

		LoginItemsList - Model class representing the Login Items list

	}

	

}

Status Meu MVC {

	[NSStatusBarItem - View class that displays the application's status item]

	StatusItemController - Controller class that handles showing/hiding status item and status menu actions

	BOOL shouldDisplayStatusItem - Model

}

Behavioral Values:
	(float) corner avoidance distance - Prefs
	(BOOL) Master on/off switch (Must be On to wrap) - Status Menu
	(BOOL) Hidden on/off switch (Must be On to wrap) - Primary
	(int) "never" hotkey (Overrides everything) - Prefs
	(int) "always" hotkey (Overrides wrapping edges and application list only) - Prefs
	(BOOL) application list pos/neg - Prefs
	(Array) hot application list - Prefs
	(Array) wrapping edges - Prefs

Other Values:
	(BOOL) status item visible - Prefs
	(BOOL) launch at login - Prefs

